                                        <Path Data="M5.24031 0.5H0.5V13.5H15.5V3H7.24031L5.24031 0.5ZM1.5 12.5V1.5H4.75969L6.75969 4H14.5V12.5H1.5ZM4 6.5H12V5.5H4V6.5Z" Fill="Black"></Path>
